Trade/Device Name(s): Stat Profile® Prime ABG Analyzer System
Stat Profile® Prime Auto QC Cartridge ABG
Stat Profile® Prime Ampuled Control ABG/CCS
Stat Profile® Prime Calibrator Cartridge ABG
Regulation Name(s): Blood gases (PCO2, PO2) and blood pH test system
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): Stat Profile® Prime ABG Analyzer System
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Stat Profile Prime ABG Analyzer System and associated calibrator/control cartridges for quantitative measurement of blood gases and pH in clinical laboratory whole blood specimens.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for in vitro diagnostic use by healthcare professionals in clinical laboratories for quantitative determination of pH, PCO2, and PO2 in heparinized whole blood, and for associated calibration and quality control of the analyzer system.
